==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ashen
<hw>Ash"en</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consisting of, or resembling, ashes;
of a color between brown and gray, or white and gray.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>ashen</qex> hue of age.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

